\s Ee ninataka kusikia
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ee ninataka kusikia \bd*\bd j\bd*\bd uu ya \bd*\bd Neema\bd*\bd  yake Bwana, Yeye aliyekufa kwami, maana ananipenda sana.\bd*
\pc \bdit Habari za Yesu, habari za Yesu, Na za \bdit*\bdit Mapendo yake\bdit*\bdit  kwami, ninafurahi kusikia.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ee ninataka kutambua vile mapenzi yake Bwana, Ili nijue kumufuata, kumutukuza sikuzote.\bd*
\pc \bdit Habari za Yesu, habari za Yesu, Na za \bdit*\bdit Mapendo yake\bdit*\bdit  kwami, ninafurahi kusikia.\bdit*
